@Node "AllocSignal"

   @{b}AllocSignal@{plain}

   Usage: sigBit = AllocSignal()
   -

   Allocates an returns a signal bit.
   The mask to wait for is 2**sigBit.

   Returns -1 for failure

   See @{"CheckSignal" LINK "CheckSignal"} @{"FreeSignal" LINK "FreeSignal"} @{"signal" LINK "signal"} @{"wait" LINK "wait"} .
@EndNode

