   @{b}SetComment@{plain}

   Usage: res = SetComment(file,comment)
   <file>,<comment>

   Sets the "comment" of "file" . "file2 is an AmigaDOS file name with path, not
   an ARexx file name.

   Returns an ARexx boolean.
