   @{b}SetOwner@{plain}

   Usage: res = SetOwner(file,GID,UID)
   <file>,<GID/N>,<UID/N>

   Sets the group id and the user id of "file" .
   "file" is an AmigaDOS file with path not an ARexx file name.
