   @{b}SetVar@{plain}

   Usage: res = SetVar(name,value,options)
   <name>,<value>,[options]

   Sets the var "name" to "value" .

   If present, options is one or more of:
   - VAR
   - ALIAS
   - IGNORE
   - GLOBAL
   - BINARY
   - NTNULL
   - SAVE
   e.g. "VAR GLOBAL"
   The default is "VAR GLOBAL"

