   @{b}SubTime@{plain}

   Usage: call SubTime(time1,time2)
   <time1/V>,<time2/V>

   Subtracts "time1" to "time2" , result in "time2", both timeval structures.

   See @{"AddTime" LINK "AddTime"} @{"CmpTime" LINK "CmpTime"} @{"GetSysTime" LINK "GetSysTime"} @{"SetSysTime" LINK "SetSysTime"} .
